venue.name: Empire State Building 86th Floor Observation Deck

tip.text: Budget 3 star hotel. Rooms are cosy/comfy. The rooftop pool has an excellent view of the ocean if u can ignore the surrounding upcoming high rise buildings and the god-awful poor pool tiling selection

formattedAddress: Lot OB 3LG 1.5 & 1.6, Oasis Boulevard (3, Jln PJS 11/15,Sunway Pyramid)

tip.text: The tea here is awesome. Definitely a must try if you are a tea fanatic. Try the butter beer (not really beer) and the tea champagne.
Planning lunch while visiting Prague Castle? Go here for a beautiful panoramic view of Prague city and the good food.
